Saving Throw: None

A Glyph of Spell Storing is a ward which stores a spell and releases it upon each hostile creature that enters the warded area. When this spell is cast, the caster stores a single 1st-level spell in the glyph, which is placed on a circular, 9-ft. radius area of the caster's choice. When a hostile creature passes within 9 feet of the glyph, it explodes, releasing a copy of the stored spell on each hostile creature within 12 feet.~
@34358=~Familiar Spell
