This spell brings forth a magical rain that saturates the area of effect. All creatures in the rain gain +50% fire resistance and +25% magical fire resistance. In addition, all electricity damage dealt by creatures in the rain is increased by 50%. Fire elementals, fire salamanders, and efreet in the rain take 2d3 magical cold damage every second. Flame Blade, Shroud of Flame, and salamander auras are extinguished by Cloudburst.~
@42326=~Mold Touch
