Saving Throw: Special

This spell creates a small whirlwind within the caster's sight. The whirlwind will fly around randomly, harming friend and foe alike. The caster is immune to <PRO_HISHER> own spell, and elementals and other huge creatures are also unaffected. If a creature is caught in the path of the whirlwind, it takes 4d8 crushing damage, 4d8 slashing damage, and must make a Save vs. Breath Weapon at -3 or be stunned for 2 rounds. A maximum of 8 targets can be affected, after which the whirlwind will dissipate.~
@42618=~Spiritual Wrath
