Upon completion of this spell, the priest becomes a focus of spiritual energy, which then shoots out from the caster in four directions, like lightning bolts. All creatures in the bolts' paths take 7d10 points of magic damage (save vs. Spell at -4 for half). Creatures of the same moral alignment (good, neutral, evil) as the caster are unaffected by the spell.~
@42714=~Symbol, Pain
(Conjuration/Summoning)

Level: 7
Sphere: Guardian
Range: Visual range of the caster
Duration: 11 turns
Casting Time: 3
Area of Effect: 15-ft. radius
Saving Throw: None

All enemies within 15 ft. of the symbol of pain at the moment it is invoked are overwhelmed by pain, suffering a -4 penalty to their attack rolls, a -2 penalty to their Dexterity scores, and a -2 penalty to their Armor Class.~
